    "Figure 7) displays two composite time series: the PMOD/WRC composite (CPMDF [161]) and the so-called \"community consensus\" time series [155].",
    "These composite time series are Fig. 7.",
    "PMOD/WRC composite (CPMDF, purple) based on merging 41 years of TSI measurements.",
    "For comparison, we display another composite the C1 [155] (grey line).",
    "A 30-day running mean of CPMDF is shown as a orange dashed line."
